cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.DM, cs.SI, cs.AI. 

The paper presents an algorithm for constructing coresets for large-scale SVM training, which is a problem in machine learning and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics). The paper also discusses the applicability of the algorithm to streaming, distributed, and dynamic data settings, which suggests a possible fit with cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
